title: Key West Brewfest
date: From Tuesday, September 1, 2015 to Monday, November 30, 2015
description: More than 40 species of fish are targeted during these months, with divisions for men, women, junior anglers (ages 10 to 14) and Pee Wees (under 10 years old). All participating anglers receive certificates noting their catches and qualify for a variety of prizes.
seo_description: The 9th annual BrewFest is coming Labor Day.
short_description: The 9th annual BrewFest is coming Labor Day weekend.
contents: The 9th annual BrewFest is coming Labor Day weekend 2018. Taste over 200 beers with your toes in the sand on South Beach, Key West. Enjoy pool parties, including one hosted on property Sunday, September 2nd here at the Marker, beer dinners, seminars and so much more!
